n</placeName><date when="1918-04-21" n="01">21. 4. 1918</date></correspAction><correspAction type="received"><persName ref="#pmb2121">Schnitzler, Arthur</persName><placeName ref="#pmb50">Wien</placeName></correspAction><correspContext><tei:ref type="belongsToCorrespondence" target="#pmb11002">Braun, Felix</tei:ref><ref subtype="previous_letter" type="withinCorrespondence" target="1918-04-19_01">Schnitzler an Braun, 19. 4. 1918</ref><ref subtype="next_letter" type="withinCorrespondence" target="1922-05-13_02">Braun an Schnitzler, 13. 5. 1922</ref></correspContext></correspDesc></profileDesc><encodingDesc><refsDecl><ab>References to Arthur Schnitzler’s diary online consist of the relevant dates only, 
